A concert hall interior bathed in deep blue stage lighting, where silhouetted figures of performers covered entirely in blue paint stand frozen mid-performance against dramatic spotlights, their forms creating striking shadows across a massive curved stage, while an unseen audience's energy is suggested by subtle lens flares and atmospheric haze, the scene captured in photorealistic style with rich cobalt and electric blue tones dominating the frame, theatrical fog rolling across the polished stage floor, architectural elements of a grand convention center visible in the background with sweeping modern curves and industrial rigging overhead.
